    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="695153484">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-695153484" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-695153484" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="695153484">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/36126620/">Scipio</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-07-01</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">其实讲的本质内容综合了《老子》和《韩非子》。而韩非子受教于荀子，荀子得道于黄老学，黄老学才是道家的显学。因为老子幽眇精深，无法直接应用，故黄老与庄子各得其注，黄老注之度人，庄子注之度己。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="432019561">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-432019561" class="vote-count">0</span>
